      * Leser tilbake en side
      *
     c                   eval      w_stel = 0
      *
     c                   dou       w_stel = w_ssrn + c_sfil
      *
     c                   readp     vgkpi1
      *
     c                   if        %eof or
     c                             vgfirm <> w_firm
     c                   leave
     c                   endif
